<img src="/images/community/tutorials/meraki-guide/meraki-box.jpg" />
</div>

<p>Finally youâ€™ll need to change your splash page to use a <b>custom url</b>.</p>

<p>Head to your <b>Box</b>â€™s page and click on the box youâ€™ve just added. If you donâ€™t immediately see a large green button called <b>Radius Settings</b>, youâ€™ll need to make a few changes by clicking on <b>Settings</b>.</p>

<div class="mdl-typography--text-center">
