<p><b>Note</b>: If you have tagged logins enabled, this will take priority over the URL provided.</p>

<p>Your SSID should now show in your networks. Select the SSID in your networks to test this.</p>

<p><b>!! IMPORTANT !! The SSID of your network will be the one youâ€™ve set in Meraki not the one set in CT WiFi. This feature is not available for Meraki boxes. You can rename or edit these under your Meraki SSID settings.</b></p>

<p>For multiple SSIDâ€™s, enable the SSIDâ€™s you want in your Meraki SSID settings, then return to Splash Page settings in Meraki and apply the same method as shown below.</p>

